ED_Title: Proposed programme of work and timetable of the Special Political and Decolonization Committee (Fourth Committee) for the seventy-second session of the General Assembly
ED_Plenary_Committee: Special Political and Decolonization Committee (Fourth Committee)
ED_OriginatingBody: Special Political and Decolonization Committee (Fourth Committee)
ED_DecisionText:
At its 53rd plenary meeting, on 6 December 2016, the General Assembly, on the recommendation of the Special Political and Decolonization Committee (Fourth Committee),  approved the proposed programme of work and timetable of the Fourth Committee for the seventy-second session of the Assembly as set out in the report of the Fourth Committee. 

(See A/71/503, para. 5; A/71/PV.53)
ED_Disclaimer: The text of this decision is available in all languages in document A/71/49 (Vol. II).
